            <div class="row __center">
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 col-xl-6">
                    <div class="usercontent">
                        <h4><strong>Conducting research</strong></h4>
<p><strong>We have conducted several key pieces of research over the years on areas relating to businesses and charities. We have worked with several independent research companies. </strong></p>
<p>The reports below show that the Welsh language can offer a variety of benefits, but they also highlight the difficulties and challenges. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


