                        <div class="imagetext-body">
                            <div class="usercontent">
                                <p><a href="/media/14nla5hm/bwyd-a-diod-food-and-drink.pdf" title="Bwyd A Diod Food And Drink"><strong>The value of the Welsh language to the food and drink sector in Wales</strong></a></p>
<p>Wales is acknowledged for its high-quality food and drinks produce, but what role can the Welsh language play?</p>
<p>A variety of businesses across Wales were asked about their use of the Welsh language - from branding and marketing to customer services and staffing - to better understand the value of the Welsh language to their business.</p>
