    <section class="flexibleblocks-block __nomargin">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row offset-xl-1">
                <div class="col-12 col-xl-11">
                    <div class="imagetext __animate __alt">
                            <div class="imagetext-image">
                                <img src="/media/jdydshjk/29062021comisiynyddygymraeg5729.jpg?anchor=center&amp;mode=crop&amp;width=650&amp;height=430&amp;rnd=132711596525170000" alt="Natwest welcome sign" data-object-fit="cover">
                            </div>
                        <div class="imagetext-body">
                            <div class="usercontent">
                                <p><a href="/media/ynvbdtyv/statutory-review-of-banks.pdf" title="Statutory Review Of Banks"><strong>Statutory review of the Welsh language services of the banking sector in Wales</strong></a></p>
<p>This statutory review was held following a significant rise in the number of complaints received regarding banking services. The review makes eight recommendations for the high street banks on how to improve their Welsh language services.</p>
